(12, 'Google employees join Amnesty International\'s call for Google to end its censored Chinese search engine', '<p>\"Don\'t be evil\" has transformed from a mantra into a plea.</p><p>A group of Google employees published an open letter to their employer on Tuesday, calling for an end to Google\'s planned censored Chinese search engine. The 11 co-signees are mostly engineers and joined Amnesty International\'s day of action criticizing Google\'s creation of the censored search engine.&nbsp;</p><p>Amnesty International, Google employees, and experts say that it would enable human rights abuses in China, and potentially help codify a censored internet in other countries that demand it.</p><p>\"Our opposition to Dragonfly is not about China: we object to technologies that aid the powerful in oppressing the vulnerable, wherever they may be,\" the Google employees wrote.</p><p><br></p><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-filename=\"Untitled-17.jpg\" style=\"margin: 10px; width: 545px;\"><p><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.75em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 174, 239);\">Employee protests</span></p><div class=\"fb-quote fb_iframe_widget\" fb-xfbml-state=\"rendered\" fb-iframe-plugin-query=\"app_id=122071082108&amp;container_width=950&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fmashable.com%2Farticle%2Femployee-protest-google-chinese-search-engine%2F%3Futm_cid%3Dhp-n-4&amp;locale=en_US&amp;sdk=joey\" style=\"display: inline-block; position: absolute; margin-bottom: 2rem; left: 502.5px; top: 2086px;\"><a href=\"https://mashable.com/article/google-walkout-san-francisco/\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 174, 239);\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; position: relative; text-align: justify; vertical-align: bottom; width: 169px; height: 47px;\"><iframe name=\"f21b8fc7238f7cc\" width=\"1000px\" height=\"1000px\" frameborder=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"encrypted-media\" title=\"fb:quote Facebook Social Plugin\" src=\"https://web.facebook.com/v2.8/plugins/quote.php?app_id=122071082108&amp;channel=https%3A%2F%2Fstaticxx.facebook.com%2Fconnect%2Fxd_arbiter%2Fr%2F7LloFuHvA7I.js%3Fversion%3D43%23cb%3Df2f01c57acd35d4%26domain%3Dmashable.com%26origin%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fmashable.com%252Ff3da0a4f309194%26relation%3Dparent.parent&amp;container_width=950&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fmashable.com%2Farticle%2Femployee-protest-google-chinese-search-engine%2F%3Futm_cid%3Dhp-n-4&amp;locale=en_US&amp;sdk=joey\" class=\"\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; position: absolute; visibility: visible; width: 169px; height: 47px;\"></iframe></span></a></div><p>&nbsp;on how Google handled sexual misconduct incidents, and a larger culture of discrimination at Google, recently prompted&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 174, 239);\">changes</span>&nbsp;to Google\'s sexual abuse reporting and other processes.&nbsp;</p><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.75em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;\"=\"\">That same impact of employee voices on Google policy might not apply when it comes to Project Dragonfly. But that\'s not stopping Google employees and advocates from trying.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.75em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;\"=\"\">\"Google is too powerful not to be held accountable,\" the employees wrote. \"We deserve to know what we’re building and we deserve a say in these significant decisions.\"</p>', 'published', 'false', '[{\"index\":0,\"img\":\"blog_photo_12_1.jpg\",\"thumb\":\"blog_photo_12_1_thumb.jpg\"}]', '1544072785', 'admin', 1, '[]', 4);
INSERT INTO `blog_photo` (`blog_photo_id`, `title`, `description`, `status`, `hide_status`, `img_features`, `timestamp`, `blog_photo_uploader_type`, `blog_photo_uploader_id`, `edited_by`, `view_count`) VALUES
(13, 'Facebook built Portal for friends to connect, but it has more to offer businesses', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0.75em; margin-bottom: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;\"=\"\">Are you ready for Facebook to have a physical, semi-permanent presence in your home? That\'s the central question you\'ll need to consider before you invest in the company\'s new Portal or Portal+ speaker.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.75em; margin-bottom: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;\"=\"\">The pair of speakers, Facebook\'s first non-VR hardware product, come at a time when trust in the social network is at an all-time low. The company is reeling from scandal after scandal, and is still facing tough questions about users\' privacy.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.75em; margin-bottom: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;\"=\"\">While the Portal and Portal+ are often compared to Amazon\'s Echo Show, Facebook\'s devices are actually much more limited. Yes, you can use Alexa skills, but there are very few third-party apps available for the Portal right now. There\'s Pandora, Spotify, and iHeartRadio for music, as well as YouTube, Food Network, and Facebook Watch for video.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.75em; margin-bottom: 1.5em;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.75em; margin-bottom: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;\"=\"\">But Portal is first and foremost a video-calling tool. Yes, it can technically do a bit more than that — you can add your Amazon account to use Alexa skills and perhaps future functionality —&nbsp; but if you\'re not planning on spending a lot of time video chatting, there\'s no point in getting one.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.75em; margin-bottom: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;\"=\"\"><br></span></p><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-filename=\"Untitled-12.jpg\" style=\"margin: 10px; width: 545px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0.75em; margin-bottom: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;\"=\"\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.75em; margin-bottom: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;\"=\"\"><br></span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1rem; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" bold;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(85,=\"\" 85,=\"\" 85);=\"\" text-rendering:=\"\" optimizelegibility;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 24px;=\"\" line-height:=\"\" 1.27;=\"\" clear:=\"\" left;\"=\"\">The case for having a Portal in the office<div class=\"fb-quote fb_iframe_widget\" fb-xfbml-state=\"rendered\" fb-iframe-plugin-query=\"app_id=122071082108&amp;container_width=950&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fmashable.com%2F2018%2F12%2F05%2Ffacebook-portal-and-portal-plus-review%2F%3Futm_cid%3Dmash-prod-nav-sub-st%23NPZFF9IeZsqh&amp;locale=en_US&amp;sdk=joey\" style=\"display: inline-block; position: absolute; margin-bottom: 2rem; left: 459.5px; top: 5532px;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; position: relative; text-align: justify; vertical-align: bottom; width: 169px; height: 47px;\"><iframe name=\"f524d2f3200d4\" width=\"1000px\" height=\"1000px\" frameborder=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"encrypted-media\" title=\"fb:quote Facebook Social Plugin\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/v2.8/plugins/quote.php?app_id=122071082108&amp;channel=https%3A%2F%2Fstaticxx.facebook.com%2Fconnect%2Fxd_arbiter%2Fr%2F7LloFuHvA7I.js%3Fversion%3D43%23cb%3Df8b867237e873c%26domain%3Dmashable.com%26origin%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fmashable.com%252Ff1b09e5770c751c%26relation%3Dparent.parent&amp;container_width=950&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fmashable.com%2F2018%2F12%2F05%2Ffacebook-portal-and-portal-plus-review%2F%3Futm_cid%3Dmash-prod-nav-sub-st%23NPZFF9IeZsqh&amp;locale=en_US&amp;sdk=joey\" class=\"\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; position: absolute; visibility: visible; width: 169px; height: 47px;\"></iframe></span></div></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 0.75em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;\"=\"\">One use case where I do think Portal actually makes a lot of sense — and one Facebook hasn\'t talked about very much — is not as an in-home video calling gadget, but as a corporate video conferencing tool.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.75em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;\"=\"\">Think about it: corporate video conferencing systems tend to suck. They\'re expensive and bug-ridden and never quite work the way you need them to. And Facebook already has relationships with thousands of companies, thanks to Workplace.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.75em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;\"=\"\"><br></p><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-filename=\"Untitled-11.jpg\" style=\"margin: 10px; width: 545px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0.75em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;\"=\"\"><br></p>', 'published', 'false', '[{\"index\":0,\"img\":\"blog_photo_13_1.jpg\",\"thumb\":\"blog_photo_13_1_thumb.jpg\"}]', '1544073358', 'admin', 1, '[]', 6);
